{
  "stem": "7598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The teachers and, and the headmasters had a very rough time during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, two of the teachers were shot by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We lead a very sheltered life, I would say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother was taught just enough Hebrew to have a bar mitzvah, and I wasn't even taught Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We kept just the High Holidays, but that was about all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Until German Jews started coming out, I wasn't really aware of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My-- I had a very close girlfriend who, to my amazement, her father turned out to be a Nazi when the war broke out in 1940, and he came out in his [INAUDIBLE] uniform.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also we-- as children we used to have-- we used to play dramatics and have a little dramatic society.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we once asked-- I asked a girlfriend, you should come to tea to do a rehearsal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she told me that she was not allowed to go to a Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember this, so it must have had some impact but not tremendously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but also that was the day of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know before that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I have never seen her since.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we escaped anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I became conscious of the political situation [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] because we heard of Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have a television, but we knew about it, although it was, it was remote.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't on our doorstep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And German professors started-- particularly professors in academia-- started coming out of Germany and knocking on doors asking for jobs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which was, I remember, a very sad situation, because these people weren't trained to be in the diamond business or anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
